didnt even hear the jets roaring overhead we realized we were 
under attack when the first two planes fired four rockets 
a police spokesman said the jets dropped 250pound bombs 
the statement by the israeli military command said the planes 
raided a base of the syrianbased palestine liberation front a tiny 
plo faction founded by the late talaat yacoub who had split from 
the popular front for the liberation of palestine in the mid1970s 
