fighting in lebanons 14yearold civil war intensified after aoun 
rejected a syrian proposal for the formation of a security 
committee representing various lebanese factions to oversee 
implementation of a ceasefire 
annahar said aoun insisted on the creation of a 
lebanesesyrian security committee arguing that the 
confrontation was between syrian and lebanese forces and not among 
lebanese factions 
